WEBVTT

00:03.934 --> 00:06.539
Reduce, reuse, recycle.

00:07.097 --> 00:09.187
It's very easy to do.

00:10.081 --> 00:12.935
It's simple to remember.

00:13.099 --> 00:15.305
Recycle what you use.

00:16.309 --> 00:18.963
Separate glass and paper.

00:19.199 --> 00:21.187
Separate plastic and tin.

00:22.113 --> 00:27.288
Then put them in their places in the recycling bin.

00:28.349 --> 00:30.452
Plastic with plastic.

00:31.411 --> 00:33.401
Paper with paper.

00:34.309 --> 00:39.557
Tin with tin and glass with glass.

00:39.973 --> 00:42.981
Reduce, reuse, recycle.

00:43.097 --> 00:45.285
It's very easy to do.

00:46.154 --> 00:48.913
It's simple to remember.

00:49.125 --> 00:51.590
Recycle what you use.

00:52.319 --> 00:57.299
Separate glass and paper; separate plastic and tin.

00:58.095 --> 01:03.295
Then put them in their places in the recycling bin.

01:04.765 --> 01:05.861
Good for you.

